Koemei module for Kaltura Mediaspace
============

Version 0.2.2

Installation
--------

Copy the content of this archive into the mediaspace/modulesCustom folder

Usage
--------

1. Register on https://www.koemei.com
2. Enable the module
3. All your existing and future media will be automatically transcribed

Known issues
--------

soon...

Troubleshooting
--------

* In case your newly added media files are not automatically transcribed, please check that the notifications are setup in kmc (Settings>Integration Settings>Notifications) and that the url is https://www.koemei.com/REST/services/notify/kaltura
* Please contact support@koemei.com if you need help setting up or using this plugin.


